Scores of parents and sympathisers of children kidnapped from Bethel Baptist High School in kaduna state on Monday stormed the Kaduna-Kachia road, impeding traffics and calling for the release of their wards.
They are also requesting for the unconditional release of their kids
Recall that gunmen suspected to be kidnappers in the early hours of Monday invaded Bethel Secondary School, Maramara in Chikun Local Government Area of Kaduna State, kidnapping unspecified numbers of students
